this is the single largest investment ever made by a federal government to support access to post - secondary education for all Canadians . 
elements of the Canadian opportunities strategy , which is designed to provide Canadians with greater access to the knowledge and skills needed for jobs and opportunities in the 21 st century , are included in this bill . 
